Test-Filesystem

This test framework compare filesystems. You can use it your perl programs
are generating filesystems parts and you don't want to compare file by file.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Test::Filesystem

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Test-Filesystem

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Test-Filesystem

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Test-Filesystem

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Test-Filesystem/


